“Minister” means the Minister charged with the responsibility for
finance;
“prescribed”, unless otherwise stated, means prescribed by
regulations made under section 28;
“prescribed goods” means goods prescribed by order made under
section 6;
“proper officer of customs” shall have the same meaning as is
assigned to that expression in section 2 of the Customs Act 1967.
